{"word":"προδιδάσκω","slug":"προδιδάσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προδιδάσκω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άξω</el>) </el><p/><i>to teach</i> one a thing <i>beforehand</i>, <el>τινά τι</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>πρ. τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> et <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <el>πρ. τινὰ σοφὸν εἶναι</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to have</i> one <i>taught beforehand</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to learn beforehand</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}